---
---
<section id="about" class="relative py-32 px-6 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative side lines -->
  <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-cyan-900/50 to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-cyan-900/50 to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section label -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-16">
      <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-cyan-800/50"></div>
      <span class="font-mono text-xs text-cyan-600 tracking-widest px-4">// ABOUT THIS SITE</span>
      <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-cyan-800/50"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Text -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold leading-snug">
          <span class="text-white">魔導書</span>
          <span class="text-gray-500">として読む、</span>
          <br />
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">車載ソフトウェア</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-base">
          AUTOSARや車載ソフトウェアの技術は、複雑で難解に見えます。<br/>
          でも、その構造は魔法の体系と驚くほど似ています。
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-base">
          BSWは<span class="text-cyan-400">「世界の基盤魔術」</span>、
          RTEは<span class="text-purple-400">「召喚陣」</span>、
          SWCは<span class="text-blue-400">「術者」</span>、
          CANは<span class="text-cyan-400">「呪文の通信路」</span>—。
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-base">
          このサイトは、組み込みエンジニアの視点から、
          技術を物語として語り直す場所です。
          初心者にも、経験者にも、新しい「読み方」を提供します。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Spell book visualization -->
      <div class="relative flex justify-center">
        <div class="relative w-72 h-80">
          <!-- Outer glow -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cyan-500/5 rounded-lg blur-xl"></div>
          <!-- Card -->
          <div class="relative h-full border border-cyan-900/60 rounded-lg bg-[#0a0a1f]/80 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6 pb-4 border-b border-cyan-900/40">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-cyan-400 animate-pulse"></div>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-cyan-600 tracking-wider">AUTOSAR_STACK.hex</span>
            </div>
            <!-- Layers visualization -->
            <div class="space-y-2 font-mono text-xs">
              {[
                { label: 'Application Layer', sub: 'SWC / 術者たち', color: 'text-purple-400', border: 'border-purple-800/50', bg: 'bg-purple-950/30' },
                { label: 'Runtime Environment', sub: 'RTE / 召喚陣', color: 'text-blue-400', border: 'border-blue-800/50', bg: 'bg-blue-950/30' },
                { label: 'Basic Software', sub: 'BSW / 基盤魔術', color: 'text-cyan-400', border: 'border-cyan-800/50', bg: 'bg-cyan-950/30' },
                { label: 'Microcontroller', sub: 'ECU / 魔法石', color: 'text-green-400', border: 'border-green-800/50', bg: 'bg-green-950/30' },
              ].map(layer => (
                <div class={`px-3 py-2 rounded border ${layer.border} ${layer.bg} group hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform cursor-default`}>
                  <div class={`${layer.color} text-xs font-semibold`}>{layer.label}</div>
                  <div class="text-gray-600 text-[10px] mt-0.5">{layer.sub}</div>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
            <!-- Bottom tag -->
            <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 text-[10px] font-mono text-cyan-900">
              ✦ COMPILED OK
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
